description: Designates an account as the delegated Amazon Macie administrator account for an organization in Organizations.

parameters.name: adminAccountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID for the account to designate as the delegated Amazon Macie administrator account for the organization.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: A unique, case-sensitive token that you provide to ensure the idempotency of the request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.
